to install virtualenv 
python -m pip install --user virtualenv


1)to create virtual environment command is:-
     cd Desktop/test
python3 -m virtualenv env



2)activate virtual env by following command.
cd Desktop/test/env     
source bin/activate..


3)install flask inside virtual environment by the command      pip install flask
4)install pandas inside virtual environment by the command     pip install pandas
5)run    python app.py 
 




